description: LinqAn (LINQ ANalytics, pronounced "Lincoln") is a .NET companion library for analytics platforms, allowing for LINQ-based queries. LinqAn.Google is the Google version, which uses Google Analytics Core Reporting API v3.
summary: LinqAn (LINQ ANalytics, pronounced "Lincoln") is a .NET companion library for analytics platforms, allowing for LINQ-based queries. LinqAn.Google is the Google version, which uses Google Analytics Core Reporting API v3. Currently this supports .NET framework 4.5, in addition to DNX4.5.1.
title: LinqAn.Google
